The Garrison offers private offices and all the extras you need for your day: espresso coffee, breakfast, showers and more. Rely on the Community Team to handle your admin, field your calls, and keep you up to speed with community happenings.This opulently restored Georgian is classic with a modern edge. Think sparkling chandeliers, velvet couches, spacious-feeling art work and lots of natural light. Elegant boardrooms and an informal kitchen let you choose a professional or relaxed setting for meetings and catch-ups.Includes you in a diverse business network across Dublin 2. Let your business take flight with a base at Dublin Airport, connecting Ireland to the rest of the world. Next to Terminal 1, Skybridge House is at the centre of an international hub, with direct flights to 40 countries across the world.

Welcome clients to this ultra-modern glass building with high-spec facilities and panoramic views across the airfield and North Dublin. Find plenty to entertain you after work or at lunchtime, with the airport’s restaurants, cafes and hotels close by.
